data.text:
Total population reached 0.086 mil in 2050 in Seychelles, according to the National Statistical Office. This is 0.702% less than in the previous year.

Historically, total population in Seychelles reached an all time high of 0.099 mil in 2021 and an all time low of 0.036 mil in 1950.

Seychelles has been ranked 175th within the group of 179 countries we follow in terms of total population.
